name: THE WOMEN, THE MORNING AND THE LOOKING
description:
I'm so grateful

The pandemic really hit my family's economy, everything just felt more and more difficult, the children's school fees that were still ongoing even though learning was done at home, the cost of renting, plus the cost of daily life.

But since Pakal's City forest was inaugurated, I've been helped. By still complying with the health protocol, visitors can come, while I am a parking guard for tourists who want to go there.

I am grateful for what has been destined, and I am happy for what I am grateful for.
